query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 1 AND q1.score <= 10
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('client-object-model',
'custom-taxonomy',
'equilibrium',
'filters',
'images',
'mortgage',
'redox',
'theme-development',
'united-kingdom')
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('chemistry',
'money',
'sharepoint',
'wordpress')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
